**GLUTEN-FREE Open-VZ and KVM VPS!**

There's nothing worse than a company exploiting a fad to profit from the lesser informed, well fear not because we're here to save the day!

Always looking for new ways to improve our product range, we've finally done it. After years of testing and refinement, we've created the Holy Grail of VPS. DireVPS are proud to present our new **GLUTEN FREE** range!

Raised on a Highland farm, near the windy shores of OpenITC Vale, just east of Sea Peue, we've crafted the finest VPS, capturing both flavour and performance that's coeliac compatible.

If you're experiencing bloating, diarrhoea, nausea, wind, constipation, tiredness, headaches, mouth ulcers, sudden or unexpected weight loss when using other VPS then you could benefit from using ours!

We guarantee our products to be GLUTEN FREE!*

Take one VPS every month for several months. This is unlikely to reduce your symptoms but will definitely not worsen your gluten allergy.

*Made on a server which has been near nuts. Whilst every effort has been made during the preparation of your VPS, some bones may still be present and could represent a choking hazard. Please consult a doctor before using if pregnant.


